  <!-- EN: victory rifle -->
  <Gun_Special_VictoryRifle.label>胜利步枪</Gun_Special_VictoryRifle.label>
  <!-- EN: An advanced scoped revolver rifle where, according to its name sake, can guarantee victory in battle. The victory rifle is equipped with an advanced scope that looks alien in nature, where upon using it, can increase their shooting accuracy, and aid the user in pinpointing the target's weak spots and brutally exploiting it. Thanks to its advanced scope, the rifle has a chance to deal stun damage, and a slim chance of inflicting a critical hit that guarantees death upon impact. -->
  <Gun_Special_VictoryRifle.description>一款配备先进瞄准镜的左轮步枪，正如其名，能确保战斗胜利。胜利步枪配备了一款外观充满外星风格的先进瞄准镜，使用时可提高射击精度，并帮助使用者精准锁定目标的弱点并予以残酷打击。 得益于其先进的瞄准镜，该步枪有一定几率造成眩晕伤害，并有极低几率触发致命一击，该一击命中即保证击杀。</Gun_Special_VictoryRifle.description>
  <Gun_Special_VictoryRifle.tools.stock.label>库存</Gun_Special_VictoryRifle.tools.stock.label>
  <Gun_Special_VictoryRifle.tools.hook_bayonet.label>钩刺</Gun_Special_VictoryRifle.tools.hook_bayonet.label>
  <Gun_Special_VictoryRifle.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>胜利步枪</Gun_Special_VictoryRifle.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>
  <!-- EN: blood letter katana -->
  <MeleeWeapon_Special_BloodLetter.label>血字武士刀</MeleeWeapon_Special_BloodLetter.label>
  <!-- EN: An ominous katana of unknown origins. Its blade is so sharp that it can cleanly cut-off a torso in half, possess a unique property where it can cause heavy bleeding in every continuous hit, and grant faster healing to the wielder. -->
  <MeleeWeapon_Special_BloodLetter.description>一把来历不明的不祥日本刀。其刀刃锋利至极，足以将躯干一刀两断；它还具备一项独特特性：每次连续命中都会造成大量出血，并能使持刀者恢复速度加快。</MeleeWeapon_Special_BloodLetter.description>
  <!-- EN: handle -->
  <MeleeWeapon_Special_BloodLetter.tools.handle.label>手柄</MeleeWeapon_Special_BloodLetter.tools.handle.label>
  <!-- EN: point -->
  <MeleeWeapon_Special_BloodLetter.tools.point.label>点</MeleeWeapon_Special_BloodLetter.tools.point.label>
  <!-- EN: edge -->
  <MeleeWeapon_Special_BloodLetter.tools.edge.label>边缘</MeleeWeapon_Special_BloodLetter.tools.edge.label>
  <!-- EN: Captain Lud's Holy Blade -->
  <MeleeWeapon_Special_CaptainLudsHolyBlade.label>卢德船长的圣刃</MeleeWeapon_Special_CaptainLudsHolyBlade.label>
  <!-- EN: A two-handed greatsword replica of the original weapon, that was wielded by the legendary captain of the hunters covenant named "Captain Lud". The replica is a unique incendiary greatsword capable of setting a single target on fire, along with the ability of rendering their heat armor in-effective, and making them extremely vulnerable to fire upon impact.\n\nAccording to ancient records, the original "Captain Lud's Holy Blade" were created in response to the ever growing sanguophage threat imposed by the Bloody Chalice led by "Vlad The Impaler", which sparked the beggining of the Covenant Crusade. -->
  <MeleeWeapon_Special_CaptainLudsHolyBlade.description>这是一把双持巨剑的复制品，原版武器曾由猎人盟约中名为“卢德船长”的传奇船长所使用。该复制品是一把独特的燃烧型巨剑，能够点燃单一目标，同时使其热能护甲失效，并在击中瞬间使其极易受到火焰伤害。

据古代记载，最初的“卢德船长的圣刃”是为了应对由“穿刺者弗拉德”领导的“血杯”组织日益加剧的嗜血者威胁而打造的，这也引发了契约十字军东征的序幕。</MeleeWeapon_Special_CaptainLudsHolyBlade.description>
  <MeleeWeapon_Special_CaptainLudsHolyBlade.tools.handle.label>手柄</MeleeWeapon_Special_CaptainLudsHolyBlade.tools.handle.label>
  <MeleeWeapon_Special_CaptainLudsHolyBlade.tools.point.label>点</MeleeWeapon_Special_CaptainLudsHolyBlade.tools.point.label>
  <!-- EN: fiery edge -->
  <MeleeWeapon_Special_CaptainLudsHolyBlade.tools.fiery_edge.label>烈焰边缘</MeleeWeapon_Special_CaptainLudsHolyBlade.tools.fiery_edge.label>
